{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.760", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.920", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass Entwicklungszusammenarbeit nicht immer leicht verst\u00e4ndlich ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.760", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wissen wir aus vielen Gespr\u00e4chen mit B\u00fcrgern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe allerdings mittlerweile das Gef\u00fchl, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.440", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieser Bereich auch von der Bundesregierung nicht wirklich verstanden wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.800", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesen Eindruck macht zumindest der derzeitige Haushaltsentwurf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.160", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der wenig Neues und wenig Weitblick enth\u00e4lt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie bisher setzt der Minister im Kern auf bilaterale Zusammenarbeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.960", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei sind die Herausforderungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.320", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor denen die Welt steht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.640", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "viel zu komplex, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.200", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um sie im Alleingang l\u00f6sen zu k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.800", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr M\u00fcller, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.400", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Bundeskanzlerin hat heute Vormittag von der Krise des Multilateralismus gesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.920", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Haushalt Ihres Hauses ist doch die in Zahlen manifestierte Krise des Multilateralismus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie selbst verursachen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.880", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um Entwicklungszusammenarbeit klug, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.080", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "effizient und nachhaltig zu gestalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.000", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss Deutschland europ\u00e4isch und multilateral handeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.720", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn nur wenn alle gemeinsam an einem Strang ziehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.080", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnen weltweite Probleme wirklich angegangen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieses w\u00fcrde in der Konsequenz allerdings bedeuten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.680", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Mittel f\u00fcr die bilaterale Zusammenarbeit deutlich verringert und im Gegenzug die Mittel f\u00fcr die multilaterale Zusammenarbeit deutlich aufgestockt werden m\u00fcssten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.640", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und genau das tun Sie eben nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie stocken die bilateralen Mittel sogar noch auf und handeln damit entgegen dem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.320", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Ihre Kanzlerin Ihnen heute ins Buch geschrieben hat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.400", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das zeigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Bundesregierung die internationale Dimension der Entwicklungszusammenarbeit nicht einmal ansatzweise verstanden hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.920", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Statt unserem \u201eDenken wir neu\u201c kommt von Ihnen nur ein klares Weiter-so."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.120", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wichtiger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.680", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als immer mehr Geld zur Verf\u00fcgung zu stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.200", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind Programme in Entwicklungsl\u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.320", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich an der Wirksamkeit orientieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.840", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei muss auch immer wieder \u00fcberpr\u00fcft werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob das Geld tats\u00e4chlich geholfen hat und ob die Projekte vor Ort wirklich erfolgreich und nachhaltig waren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.240", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier fordern wir glasklare Transparenz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.560", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Uns geht es doch darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Menschen in ihren Heimatl\u00e4ndern eine Perspektive zu bieten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.280", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Reden wir nicht drumherum: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.600", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht auch um Fluchtursachenbek\u00e4mpfung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber glauben wir wirklich und tats\u00e4chlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.480", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir 67\u00a0Millionen Fl\u00fcchtlingen eine bessere Perspektive bieten k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.960", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir allein ein paar 100\u00a0Millionen Euro mehr zur Verf\u00fcgung stellen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.240", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur wenn sich die Lebensbedingungen f\u00fcr Menschen in Entwicklungsl\u00e4ndern wirklich zum Besseren wenden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.720", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird der Migrationsdruck abnehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.960", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist eine Generationenaufgabe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.280", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der wir uns stellen m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.600", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr Afrika hat die Bundesregierung hierzu einen sogenannten Marshallplan vorgelegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.400", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser ist bisher allerdings reine Schaufensterpolitik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.720", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jedem ist doch klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.360", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur gemeinsam mit der EU und multilateralen Organisationen kann dieser Plan erfolgreich umgesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.120", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier gilt einfach wieder: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.200", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alleine wird Deutschland wenig bewegen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.000", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mehr Investitionen in internationale Bildungsprogramme w\u00e4ren ja vielleicht eine gute Idee. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.600", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Weber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.160", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Steffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.960", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich nehme Sie beim Wort. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.560", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bisher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.120", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.360", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommt die F\u00f6rderung von Grundbildung in der deutschen Entwicklungspolitik viel zu kurz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.800", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei schafft doch gerade Grundbildung die Grundlage f\u00fcr das gesamte weitere Leben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.960", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Investieren Sie endlich mehr Geld in die Grundbildung! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur wer lesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.880", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schreiben und rechnen kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.760", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist in der Lage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.880", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sp\u00e4ter einen Beruf zu erlernen und vor allen Dingen ein selbstbestimmtes Leben zu f\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.960", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir dabei sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.520", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber Bek\u00e4mpfung von Fluchtursachen zu sprechen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.800", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Riesige Waldfl\u00e4chen gehen jedes Jahr durch Brandrodung verloren und m\u00fcssten durch Aufforstung zur\u00fcckgeholt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.480", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.880", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sprechen doch immer von der Bewahrung der g\u00f6ttlichen Sch\u00f6pfung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.680", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber auch das wird Deutschland nicht allein bew\u00e4ltigen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.520", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die weltweite Aufforstung kann nur international gelingen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.240", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Steigern Sie die multilateralen Mittel f\u00fcr diesen Bereich!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.680", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch ein letzter Punkt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.000", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade Frauen sind in Entwicklungsl\u00e4ndern von einem fehlenden medizinischen Angebot im Bereich der Familienplanung betroffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.360", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Familienplanung ist in den Entwicklungsl\u00e4ndern jedoch deshalb besonders wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.560", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit es nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.640", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie von der Deutschen Stiftung Weltbev\u00f6lkerung prognostiziert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.520", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bis 2050 zu einer Verdoppelung der Bev\u00f6lkerung in Afrika kommt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.880", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die USA haben ihre Beitr\u00e4ge zum Bev\u00f6lkerungsfonds der UN leider Gottes vollst\u00e4ndig eingestellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.400", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier muss Deutschland die Herausforderung mit annehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.880", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier kommt von Ihnen genau nichts, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.880", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es darum geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.600", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit den europ\u00e4ischen Partnern gemeinsam zu handeln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.840", 
   "id": "s000088", 
